OL,3,CNew Channel Island alliance created to
OL,4,Ctackle health challenges
OL,6,FJersey's Health Minister, Deputy Tom
OL,7,FBinet, said: "It is becoming
OL,8,Fincreasingly important for our islands
OL,9,Fto share resources and information
OL,10,Fthat will strengthen the
OL,11,Fsustainability of our health and
OL,12,Fsocial care services and provide
OL,13,Fgreater value for money."
OL,15,FThe alliance will be made up of senior
OL,16,Fstaff from both islands who will meet
OL,17,Fsix times a year to focus on one core
OL,18,Farea to improve.
